[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "無事にとうちゃーく！\nヴィアベル州ー！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "ここから先は、お前たちだけで行ってこい。\n俺は船を見ておかなきゃならんからな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "そうなのね。分かった。\nここまで乗せてくれてありがとう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "ああ。紀行文、楽しみにしてるぜ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "早速海に入るのもいいけど……\nまずはヴィアベル州を探検してみようよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "はしゃぎすぎて迷子にならないでよね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "人が多いから、本当に迷子になっちゃいそう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "人が集まってるあそこで、何かやってるみたいね。\n見に行ってみましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "地元の子どもたちによる、劇でしょうか。\nヴィアベル州は芸術が盛んだと聞いているけど……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "題名『海底の涙』、だって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "この州の伝承と同じ題名ね。さっき聞いたのだけれど、\n海の底にお宝が眠っているって言い伝えらしいわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "へぇー！　お宝！\nこれはトレジャーハンター、ユリエさんの出番か！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "そうね、惹かれるものがあるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "演者",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "「潮が引き――\n　進むべき道の先、竜が私を招き入れ――」",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "ユリエさん、何か気になることが？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "……こういう伝承をもとにした劇には、\n何かしらの手掛かりが隠れていることが多いの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "トレジャーハンターにとって、伝承や言い伝えは、\nお宝の在り処を示す暗号みたいなもの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……本当にお宝があると思う？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "分からない。\nでも、調べてみる価値はあるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "わたしも、気になります。\nもし本当に何かが見つかったら……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "あたしもワクワクしてきた！　\nみんなでお宝探し、やってみようよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……まあ、紀行文のネタにはなるかもね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "決まりね。\n潮が引く夜を待って、海辺を調べてみましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "やったー！　冒険の始まりだね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "うん！　みんなで力を合わせよう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……調子に乗って、ケガしないようにね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]